{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Steam Dalam Ancaman Blokir Pemerintah: Akankah Lord GabeN Bertindak?","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Belakangan ini di kalangan PC gamers Indonesia sedang ramai soal berita akan diblokirnya platform toko software digital Steam milik Valve. Steam populer di kalangan gamers yang mengonsumsi game ataupun software digital asli non bajakan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ini dipicu oleh <em>statement</em> badan klasifikasi/rating game terbaru Indonesia, IGRS (alias Indonesia Game Rating System) yang menyatakan kalau semua game yang beredar di Republik Indonesia wajib memiliki tanda rating yang dikeluarkan oleh IGRS.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27056\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27056\" data-attachment-id=\"27056\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-19-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-19-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IGRS. Badan rating video game Indonesia buatan pemerintah. Sumber gambar: sewugame.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-19-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-19-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27056\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-19-2.jpg\" alt=\"IGRS. Badan rating video game Indonesia buatan pemerintah. Sumber gambar: sewugame.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27056\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">IGRS. Badan rating video game Indonesia buatan pemerintah. Sumber gambar: sewugame.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Selama ini game-game yang dijual oleh toko digital Steam tidak memiliki tanda rating dari IGRS dan hanya menggunakan tanda rating dari negara asal game tersebut dijual, yakni Amerika Serikat, yang menggunakan tanda rating dari ESRB.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27017\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27017\" data-attachment-id=\"27017\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-6-45/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Badan rating software games Amerika Serikat. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Badan rating software games Amerika Serikat. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27017\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-12.jpg\" alt=\"Badan rating software games Amerika Serikat. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27017\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Badan rating software games Amerika Serikat. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seperti yang mungkin bro sis gamers sudah ketahui, badan pemberi rating untuk video game bukan hal baru di negara maju.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika di Amerika Serikat mereka punya ESRB (Entertainment Software Rating Board), di Jepang ada CERO (Computer Entertainment Rating Organization). Di Eropa badan ini dikenal dengan nama PEGI (Pan European Game Information).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27005\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27005\" data-attachment-id=\"27005\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-3-63/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Badan rating game Jepang. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Badan rating game Jepang. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27005\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-19.jpg\" alt=\"Badan rating game Jepang. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27005\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Badan rating game Jepang. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27032\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27032\" data-attachment-id=\"27032\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-11-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-11-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Badan rating game Eropa. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Badan rating game Eropa. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-11-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-11-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27032\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-11-7.jpg\" alt=\"Badan rating game Eropa. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27032\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Badan rating game Eropa. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Badan-badan ini merupakan organisasi <em>self-regulatory non-profit</em> (kecuali IGRS, yang merupakan badan pemerintah melalui Kementerian Komunikasi &amp; Informatika) yang bertujuan memberikan “kelas/klasifikasi/penggolongan” pada video game yang dijual di daerah di mana mereka berkuasa.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Karena masing-masing badan punya area dan pemahaman sendiri soal rating, maka jadi tidak mengherankan kalau satu game yang sama bisa berbeda tingkatan rating-nya di dua negara yang berbeda.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27053\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27053\" data-attachment-id=\"27053\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-18-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-18-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Xenoblade 2 mendapatkan rating ESRB T alias Teen. Sumber gambar: nichegamer.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Xenoblade 2 mendapatkan rating ESRB T alias Teen. Sumber gambar: nichegamer.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-18-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-18-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27053\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-18-3.jpg\" alt=\"Xenoblade 2 mendapatkan rating ESRB T alias Teen. Sumber gambar: nichegamer.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27053\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xenoblade 2 mendapatkan rating ESRB T alias Teen. Sumber gambar: nichegamer.com</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27050\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27050\" data-attachment-id=\"27050\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-17-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-17-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sementara di Jepang game ini mendapatkan rating C (15 tahun keatas) dari CERO. Sumber gambar: gonintendo.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sementara di Jepang game ini mendapatkan rating C (15 tahun keatas) dari CERO. Sumber gambar: gonintendo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-17-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-17-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27050\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-17-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sementara di Jepang game ini mendapatkan rating C (15 tahun keatas) dari CERO. Sumber gambar: gonintendo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27050\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sementara di Jepang game ini mendapatkan rating C (15 tahun ke atas) dari CERO. Sumber gambar: gonintendo.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Toko digital Steam dari perusahaan Amerika Serikat Valve, dengan bos mereka yang terkenal Gabe Newell (sering diparodikan di kalangan fans sebagai Lord GabeN), memakai sistem rating yang berlaku di Amerika Serikat alias ESRB. Hal ini yang menyebabkan pemerintah RI melalui badan rating buatan Kementerian Komunikasi &amp; Informatika, IGRS, merasa kalau Steam melanggar peraturan yang mereka buat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27026\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27026\" data-attachment-id=\"27026\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-9-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gabe Newell. Boss Valve yang juga pemilik Steam. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gabe Newell. Boss Valve yang juga pemilik Steam. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27026\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-9-8.jpg\" alt=\"Gabe Newell. Boss Valve yang juga pemilik Steam. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27026\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gabe Newell. Boss Valve yang juga pemilik Steam. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dengan kata lain, jika Steam masih ingin berjualan di wilayah hukum Republik Indonesia, mereka diwajibkan mengadopsi sistem rating IGRS yang baru diresmikan Agustus 2016 lalu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dan tentu saja keinginan IGRS tersebut dibarengi dengan ancaman pemblokiran jika pihak Steam tidak <em>comply</em> alias patuh pada regulasi yang diterapkan oleh pemerintah RI melalui IGRS.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hal ini ditegaskan oleh Samuel Abrijani Pangerapan, Direktur Jenderal Aplikasi Dan Informatika dari Kemenkominfo sebagai induk dari IGRS. Menurut Samuel, <em>guideline</em> dan <em>rules</em> dari IGRS harus menjadi acuan publisher/penerbit game yang berjualan di Indonesia. Tidak peduli apakah game tersebut buatan lokal maupun luar negeri. Atau apakah format game itu berupa hardcopy (disc) atau softcopy (executable files). Semua game harus mendapatkan label dan restu dari IGRS sebelum dapat dijual di wilayah hukum Republik Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27047\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27047\" data-attachment-id=\"27047\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-16-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-16-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dirjen Aplikasi dan Informatika Kemenkominfo. Sumber gambar: duniaku.net\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dirjen Aplikasi dan Informatika Kemenkominfo. Sumber gambar: duniaku.net&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-16-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-16-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27047\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-16-3.jpg\" alt=\"Dirjen Aplikasi dan Informatika Kemenkominfo. Sumber gambar: duniaku.net\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27047\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dirjen Aplikasi dan Informatika Kemenkominfo. Sumber gambar: duniaku.net</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Resiko terkena blokir pada Steam muncul karena games yang dijual di toko digital Lord GabeN ini belum ada yang menyematkan logo rating sesuai guideline rules dari IGRS.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kategori games yang diciptakan oleh IGRS tidak jauh berbeda dengan kompatriotnya dari luar negeri. IGRS mengusung lima jenis kategori untuk game berdasarkan usia, yaitu usia 3+ , 7+ , 13+ , 18+ dan semua umur.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27023\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27023\" data-attachment-id=\"27023\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/attachment/isi-8-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kategori IGRS sesuai urutan. Sumber gambar: kominfo.go.id\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kategori IGRS sesuai urutan. Sumber gambar: kominfo.go.id&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27023\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-8-8.jpg\" alt=\"Kategori IGRS sesuai urutan. Sumber gambar: kominfo.go.id\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27023\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kategori IGRS sesuai urutan. Sumber gambar: kominfo.go.id</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Semua games yang beredar di Indonesia wajib memiliki logo IGRS ini. Termasuk games yang ada di toko digital Steam. Jika tidak, Steam diancam akan diblokir operasinya di Indonesia.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lantas apa reaksi dari perusahaan Gabe Newell tersebut akan ancaman pemerintah RI melalui IGRS?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sampai tulisan ini saya buat, belum ada <em>statement</em> resmi baik dari <em>public relation</em> Valve, maupun dari Lord GabeN sendiri atas ancaman blokir IGRS pada Steam. Namun melihat baiknya volume penjualan mereka di RI, mungkin pihak Valve akan mulai menggunakan sistem rating IGRS untuk game yang mereka jual di Indonesia.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut saya pribadi sih Valve/Steam sepertinya masih menunggu hingga sistem rating IGRS berupa peraturan berpayung hukum atau UU, karena hingga saat ini sistem rating IGRS masih bersifat <em>voluntary</em> alias disarankan secara sukarela untuk diurus.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi mungkin tidak lama lagi Kemenkominfo akan memaksakan sistem IGRS sehingga kelak pengurusan sistem rating IGRS tidak lagi “sukarela mendaftar” melainkan “wajib mendaftar”. Kita tunggu saja ya, bro sis!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"3afa9bf9-ab6a-57c2-bf93-a7cb9cbba4a0"}}}